title: Angels - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/23/21

description:
George Noory and author Michael Lichens explore his research into angels, the role they play in protecting us from danger and preparing us for death, the fallen angels that serve Satan on Earth, as well as George's own possible encounter with an angel as a child.
